The ACUTX Mobile App can be easily accessed on Android devices. Check transaction history, account balances, pay bills, make transfers and locate our nearest ATMs and branches all in the palm of your hand.

• Fingerprint Authentication
• Bill Pay
• Remote Deposit*
• Text Alerts
• Card Controls
• Google & Samsung Pay
• Member to Member transfers

creator: Associated Credit Union of Texas
descriptionHtml:
The ACUTX Mobile App can be easily accessed on Android devices. Check transaction history, account balances, pay bills, make transfers and locate our nearest ATMs and branches all in the palm of your hand.

Additional features include:
• Fingerprint Authentication
• Bill Pay
• Remote Deposit*
• Text Alerts
• Card Controls
• Google & Samsung Pay
• Member to Member transfers

*Subject to Approval. Not available for the first 30 days after checking account opening. Not available to 180 Checking Accounts, Access Pre-Paid Cards, or Non-Profit Organization/Club Checking Business Accounts.
